## ğŸ“± Secure Authentication Made Easy! ğŸ“±

![TOTP Generator]()

This standalone TOTP (Time-based One-Time Password) generator creates secure authentication codes for your favorite services that support 2FA. No more fumbling with your phone or dealing with app permissions - just a dedicated device that provides authentication codes whenever you need them!

## âœ¨ Features âœ¨

- ğŸŒ **Easy WiFi Setup**: Configure via captive portal, no hardcoding required
- ğŸ”„ **Custom TOTP URL**: Paste any OTP Auth URL through the configuration portal  
- ğŸ“Š **Visual Timer**: Countdown bar shows time remaining before code changes
- ğŸ”„ **Auto-Refreshing Codes**: Generates new codes every 30 seconds
- ğŸ•’ **NTP Time Sync**: Ensures accurate time for proper code generation
- ğŸ” **WiFi Recovery**: Automatically reconnects if connection drops
- ğŸ”§ **Physical Reset**: Hold button for 5 seconds to enter configuration mode
- ğŸ“± **Standalone**: Works anywhere with WiFi access

